anti is also capable of aiding the company by keeping up with the channels. One of Ivanti’s features Xtraction consolidates data from multiple sources and tools and presents it in one place which aids data management. Pre-built data connectors mean no coding, no BI gurus, and no spreadsheets. The Xtraction dashboards also help showcase the work each team is doing, so management sees success and understands more clearly the priorities worked on.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">When the company also integrates operational security measures as part of the company’s endpoint and workspace management, it gives the company security controls over AV, device control, application control, and sophisticated privilege management. OS and third-party application patching is a simple, quick add-on and integrate into the same management console for a seamless experience that secure end-user devices without interfering with user productivity. Ivanti Unified Endpoint Manager—Ivanti UEM or IUEM— is targeted to increase user and IT productivity by helping IT administrators gather detailed device data, automate software and OS deployments, personalize workspace environments, and fix user issues quickly. Ivanti UEM, being the leading solution the software has the capabilities to extrapolate and manage the user profile, so it can be on any Windows device while letting IT analysts and admins do their magic for all devices from one management experience. Ivanti’s other feature Ivanti User Workspace Manager—UWM—simplifies desktop configuration, cuts IT costs, and secures user sessions while virtual, and cloud desktops. The software can make life easier for roaming users, improve login times, and forget about those GPOs and improve the overall user experience for Microsoft 365 users. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In conclusion, Ivanti Unified Endpoint Manager is intended to help companies manage devices used by the company in a unified manner no matter what software the company uses. This software is also capable of managing the device users, not just their devices to improve user productivity. If the company invests in Windows, Ivanti can help migrate and keeps the environment familiar, so readjustment is not required. Ivanti can aid the company to dig deeper, move faster, and show results. It will also become a fusion of endpoints, workspaces, and silent security. </span></p>\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For more information about Ivanti solution, </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">contact us by phone at +62 21 3861 772, by</span><a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=628111221789&amp;text=Hallo%20PT%20Realta...\"> <span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #1155cc; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Official Whatsapp</span></a><span style=\"