(8, 98, 'How to Become a Successful Software Assets Manager', 'how-to-become-a-successful-software-assets-manager', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">As technology advances, our reliance of technology increases. Companies using multiple software to run the business process is very common. However, despite the software...</span></p>', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">As technology advances, our reliance of technology increases. Companies using multiple software to run the business process is very common. However, despite the software</span> license using the same language as the region the software is deployed at, the software guidebook use language that is very challenging to understand. Understanding one software licensing is already a difficult job, let alone if deploying multiple software. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">There are different levels to understanding the company’s license position, with the highest tier version being the Effective License Position or ELP. Achieving ELP requires effort an