(11, 96, 'What is IT Asset Management', 'what-is-it-asset-management', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">IT Asset Management may have different meanings depending on the audience. This article will discuss IT Asset Management that enables the IT side of the business to run. This article will also discuss the topic of IT asset management and go over the types of tools involved, the benefits of these tools, and how to maximize the company’s expenditure in software.</span></p>', '<p><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-5751ea65-7fff-1d76-81a9-4940c25ac541\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">According to The International Association of Information Technology Asset Managers, IT Asset Management is defined as “a set of business practices that incorporates IT assets across the business units within the organization.” ITAM also includes a review of current software and hardware used, ensures licensing compliance, and tracks how IT assets are being used and where changes may be needed. An ITAM audit may aid in identifying software for which the company is over licensed or an IT asset the company is spending money on but no longer using. In today’s ever-trending world of technology, the company’s IT assets are just as valuable as financial and physical assets, if not even more so, as commerce shifts to a digital world. Therefore keeping close track of them is important to keep the company afloat. By following some IT asset management best practices in areas like asset discovery, security, governance, policy, process, metrics, and reporting an ITAM will keep business and security risks low. It will also help track trends in the IT asset lifecycle, and identify time-and-money-saving areas.</span></p>\n<p><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">There are 5 types of ITAM which are:</span></p>\n<p><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Physical</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The discovery and inventory of hardware including PCs, laptops, printers, copiers, and any other device used for IT and data management purposes.</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Digital</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The IT asset tracking of photos, videos, and digital data, including scanned hard copies.</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Software</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This area of ITAM is one that must be diligently followed, constantly reviewed, and must be fluid to meet the demands of the business, its leadership, and the changing market due to compliance issues, licensing requirements, ShadowIT (IT being installed and/or used without IT management knowledge), and IoT (the Internet of Things such as smart TVs, smart appliances, even toys). </span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Mobile</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Mobile device and data use include not only efficient applicability but also adequate security measures. Mobile devices are used more and more in the field, regardless of the industry. With that in mind, they are also the most vulnerable to Shadow IT. When the employees download apps, regardless of benefit to the company, it should be reviewed and approved by the IT management director or team based on the firm IT policies in place.</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cloud</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Use of the Cloud may eliminate the need for other hardware (servers) and software (licensing issues), not only saving the company money but also keeping data more accessible at all times.</span></p>\n<p><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ITAM stores and manages databases. There are three components to an ITAM database which are physical, financial, and contractual.</span></p>\n<p><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Physical</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The physical info is collected using tools to accept data that shows what is deployed. It will also provide visibility into all IT assets that might be in a stockroom, but not yet deployed or will be scheduled for retirement. This stockroom info is usually collected through manual processes, bar code readers, or RFID systems if they are installed.</span></p>\n<p><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Financial</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Financial data is often collected from a purchasing system or a purchase order. It indicates purchase order number, vendor name, quantity, make and model, purchase price, depreciation, cost center, and other financial attributes that an organization might need visibility into. Tracking financial attributes about an asset is useful to understand the total cost of ownership, return on investment, and assign costs to projects and IT business services.  It also helps the organization understand technical debt associated legacy applications, for example on the mainframe, and enable better decision making about end-of-life for an asset.</span></p>\n<p><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Contractual</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The third component of ITAM is contract data. This data is usually collected from the reseller directly from the vendor/supplier or a contract management system if available. It will include the information from the final negotiated version of the contract, version number, license entitlement, license type, vendor SKU, training days, service levels, maintenance, and other important contract facts. If it is a cloud or Software as a Service purchase, the details will include quantity, license type, device count, purchase price, and contract timeframe to name a few.</span></p>\n<p><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Some of the benefits achieved after IT Asset Manager implementation are:</span></p>\n<p><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Increased efficiency in project management</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Better data security</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Improved software compliance</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Better communication between business units such as sales, marketing, accounts payable, frontline staff for example</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Improved customer service through streamlined data availability</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cost reduction of IT assets through consistent review</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Streamlined budgeting process and decision-making through increased understanding of IT assets and their role in the company</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br /><br /><br /></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In conclusion, IT Asset Manager is a set of business practices that incorporates IT assets across the business units within the organization. IT Asset Management aids in the management of IT Assets to ensure that all IT assets are utilized properly. There are 5 types of ITAM which are physical, digital, software, mobile, and cloud. The three components of an ITAM database are physical, financial, and contractual. After ITAM implementation, it is expected that the companies gain benefits such as: better data security, cost reduction and increased efficiency for company processes. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><a style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\" href=\"pricing\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"images/itsm_banner.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></span></p>', '2020-12-16 06:54:51', '2021-03-27 11:02:09', 'it service management, it asset management, ITSM solution, itsm, itam, service desk', 'IT Asset Management may have different meanings depending on the audience. This article will discuss IT Asset Management that enables the IT side of the business to run. This article will also discuss the topic of IT asset management and go over the types of tools involved, the benefits of these tools, and how to maximize the company’s expenditure in software.', 71, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', '*');
INSERT INTO `itsm_blog` (`id`, `j2xml_content_id`, `j2xml_content_title`, `j2xml_content_alias`, `j2xml_content_introtext`, `j2xml_content_fulltext`, `j2xml_content_created`, `j2xml_content_modified`, `j2xml_content_metakey`, `j2xml_content_metadesc`, `j2xml_content_hits`, `j2xml_content_metadata`, `j2xml_content_language`) VALUES
(14, 95, 'Ivanti Service Manager: Deliver More Strategic Value to the Company', 'ivanti-service-manager-deliver-more-strategic-value-to-the-company', '<p class=\"intro-readmore\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Due to the demanding technological era, companies are required to be able to deliver services to customers to the utmost customer satisfaction. Therefore, the company should utilize a system that is capable of fulfilling such tasks. Also, the service utilized must be able to deliver more strategic value to the company...</span></p>', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">This is where Ivanti Service Manager comes in, an integrated set of Service and Client Management business functions that are capable of transforming service and support teams, service desks, and help desks into strategic business enablers. This multi-tenant cloud solution improves day-to-day operations and increases the agility of the business. Soon enough, this built-for-purpose, fully-automated cloud-based solution will be the company’s standard. This solution is also capable of integrated client management, service management workflow automation, and voice-enabled service desk capabilities.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><b id=\"docs-internal-guid-18579e11-7fff-89b3-47f1-e70be7ddc87b\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ivanti has a few capabilities that make the solution powerful. Comprehensive Service Management is one of them. Complete Service Management features can turn any service desk into a strategic business enabler. Providing end-to-end service management capabilities throughout the service delivery lifecycle, Ivanti is capable of executing the full-service delivery process and maintained in a low-cost cloud environment. With the Service Manager’s robust array of capabilities, your service agents and managers can quickly and successfully process and fulfill service delivery or break/fix procedures. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Some of the Comprehensive Service Management features are:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Incident Management</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Capable of capturing, identifying, and responding to issues and service requests across the organization</span> </p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Problem Management</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Able to initiate actions to correct or minimize business impact and address the root caused by focusing on known issues.</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Change Management</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Facilitates the service desk to centralize, manage, and track all assets to ensure the business goals and IT services are in constant alignment and also the ability to plan, approve, and implement changes to increase visibility and understand how each change will affect the organization.</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Release Management</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoratio