nt-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Survey</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Creates and initiates surveys so the service desk teams are able to understand the impact on their business. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ivanti does not just provide service management capabilities and processes, but also able to support more modest help desk needs. Service Manager in Cloud does not require any infrastructure,</span> <span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">and only requires limited maintenance, so help desk teams can make an immediate impact on the business. Ivanti is built to expand and grow as the company’s needs change and mature because the Service Manager is built to grow as the business grows.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><b style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> </b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;