INSERT INTO `itsm_blog` (`id`, `j2xml_content_id`, `j2xml_content_title`, `j2xml_content_alias`, `j2xml_content_introtext`, `j2xml_content_fulltext`, `j2xml_content_created`, `j2xml_content_modified`, `j2xml_content_metakey`, `j2xml_content_metadesc`, `j2xml_content_hits`, `j2xml_content_metadata`, `j2xml_content_language`) VALUES
(15, 94, 'Ivanti is Capable of Delivering More Strategic Value, Improve Service Quality, and Reduce Escalations', 'ivanti-is-capable-of-delivering-more-strategic-value-improve-service-quality-and-reduce-escalations', '<p class=\"intro-readme\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">IT management has become increasingly difficult as we become a more digitalized society. Clients expect more from IT companies. Through Ivanti Service Manager, you will gain an IT service management...</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">IT management has become increasingly difficult as we become a more digitalized society. Clients expect more from IT companies. Through Ivanti Service Manager, you will gain an IT service management </span>solution that is proven and is capable of transforming help desks and support teams to become strategic business enablers. Available on cloud and on-premise, this solution aims to improve day-to-day operations and helps IT teams achieve world-class service management for IT and other business departments.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ivanti Service Manager is capable of providing end-to-end service management at an enterprise level, enabling to deliver more strategic value. Automated workflows eliminate costly manual processes while making operations more efficient, compliant, and secure. Service Manager is also designed to be deployed quickly and scale easily to adapt as an IT company grow. Service quality could be improved significantly through Ivanti’s automation services which enable service owners and business managers to adapt, design, and take control of workflows without any coding, improving quality and consistency of services. Service desk teams can use Ivanti’s powerful diagnostic and remediation capabilities with confidence and reduce escalations. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Through Ivanti, proactive support is also possible as it leverages on cloud-based bots powered by hyper-automation and therefore easing the burden of the support team. Ivanti could automatically detect and resolve IT issues and connect proactively with customers by resolving their problems before they call. Optimizing assets becomes easier as Ivanti could automatically pre-populate the CMDB, reclaim unused software, meet compliance requirements, and save time with a centralized view of owned assets and relationships. Ivanti utilizes AI-powered bots to transform the service experience and provide self-engaging service. The bots are available 24x7 and fully integrated with Service Manager workflows to further reduce the IT team’s workload. Ivanti’s easy integration into the corporate website or employee portal, along with full mobile support, means users obtain the services they need—anytime, anywhere.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Voice automation is also possible with Ivanti since voice automation could handle calls more effectively, therefore boosting caller satisfaction. Equipped with phone-enabled self-service for resetting passwords, initiating and approving change requests, or checking service-request status it is certain that costs will be reduced. Gaining actionable insights are easy as out-of-the-box dashboards and reports provide a single view of operational, financial, and productivity metrics to help determine how well performance and business goals are met. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Flexibility between Cloud or On-Premise is not a problem as Ivanti is built on a multi-tenant technology platform designed for the cloud. Moving from one deployment model to another without losing functionality or data is very easy. With the availability of the Service Manager Mobile App, staff and users can employ their mobile devices to stay connected</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">no matter where they are. This makes it easy for staff to check on incidents, submit requests, or search for answers to IT questions. Staying connected becomes simple with the Service Manager Mobile App because staff and users can employ their mobile devices to stay connected no matter where they are. Therefore staying in touch and productive is not a problem. A modern service-delivery experience does not have to be limited to IT. In fact, it is possible to deliver enterprise services beyond IT through Ivanti. With Ivanti Service Manager, the IT team is well-positioned to automate the services and offerings of other departments. </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Partner with them to leverage your ITSM tools and practices to develop and deliver new innovative services.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In conclusion, Ivanti is capable of delivering more strategic value, improve service quality, and reduce escalations. After Ivanti’s implementation, your company will receive proactive support, optimization of your assets, and help you provide engaging self-service. Ivanti could also help your company to boost caller satisfaction and gain actionable insights. You could choose whether to implement Ivanti on Cloud or On-Premise. Staying connected using Ivanti has never been easier and delivering enterprise services beyond IT is possible.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-heig